date = datetime.strptime(date_str, "%Y-%m-%d")

date = datetime.strptime(date_str, "%Y-%m-%d")
    day = date.day

    # Use day of the month as a percentage of the month
    day_percent = day / (31 if date.month in [1, 3, 5, 7, 8, 10, 12] else 30 if date.month in [4, 6, 9, 11] else 28 if date.year % 4 == 0 else 27)

    # Determine frequency based on percentage
    freq = round(day_percent * 100)
    amplitude = 2 * np.sin(2 * np.pi * freq * np.linspace(0, 1, 1000))
    x = np.linspace(0, 1, 1000)

    plt.plot(x, amplitude)
    plt.title(f'Sine Wave for {date_str} (Frequency: {freq})')

    return plt.gca()
